item.description: I study how molecular genetics shape our behavior and risk for psychiatric illness using tools based on open-source data science. As a clinician and developmental neuropsychologist, I specialize in the evaluation of cognitive/learning/emotional difficulties and provide diagnostic clarification in children and young adults.
